e__head\">\n            <span class=\"p-form-table__required\">必須</span>希望職種\n          </dt>\n          <dd class=\"p-form-table__body\">\n            <ul class=\"p-form-table__lists\">\n              <li><label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"希望職種\" value=\"【一般管理】情報システム・社内ＳＥ職\" >【一般管理】情報システム・社内ＳＥ職</label></li>\n            </ul>\n            <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"required[]\" value=\"希望職種\">\n            \n          </dd>\n          <dt class=\"p-form-table__head\">\n            <span class=\"p-form-table__required\">必須</span>\n            お名前\n          </dt>\n          <dd class=\"p-form-table__body\">\n            <ul class=\"p-form-table__items\">\n              <li class=\"p-form-table__item\">\n                <div class=\"p-form-table__item-inner\">\n                  <span class=\"p-form-table__item-name\">姓</span>\n                  <input class=\"p-form-table__input-text\" type=\"text\" name=\"姓\" value=\"\">\n                  <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"required[]\" value=\"姓\">\n                </div>\n                \n              </li>\n              <li class=\"p-form-table__item\">\n                <div class=\"p-form-table__item-inner\">\n                  <span class=\"p-form-table__item-name\">名</span>\n                  <input class=\"p-form-table__input-text\" type=\"text\" name=\"名\" value=\"\">\n                  <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"required[]\" value=\"名\">\n                </div>\n                \n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </dd>\n          <dt class=\"p-form-table__head\">\n            <span class=\"p-form-table__required\">必須</span>\n            お名前<span class=\"p-form-table__head-sub\">（フリガナ）</span>\n          </dt>\n          <dd class=\"p-form-table__body\">\n            <ul class=\"p-form-table__items\">\n              <li class=\"p-form-table__item\">\n                <div class=\"p-form-table__item-inner\">\n                  <span class=\"p-form-table__item-name\">セイ</span>\n            